    <h3 align=center id=qname>Broom of Trilon</h3><hr size=1>
	 <table width=100% cellpadding=3 cellspacing=0 border=0>
	 <tr><td valign=top>
	 <table cellpadding=1 cellspacing=1 border=0 align=left>
	 <tr><td><b>Starts in:</b></td><td><a href='http://everquest.allakhazam.com/zones/Antonica/Solusek_Ro.htm'>Temple of Solusek Ro</a></td></tr>
	 <tr><td><b>Who:</b></td><td>Vira</a></td></tr>
	 <tr><td><b>Rating:</b></td><td>Average (3.89)</td></tr>
	 <tr><td><b>Estimated Time:</b></td><td>4 hours</td></tr>
	 <tr><td><b>Minimum Level:</b></td><td>33</td></tr><tr><td><b>Best Class:</b></td><td>Magician</td></tr><tr><td colspan=2><b>Quest Items:</b></span><li><a href="http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/item.html?item=2766">A Broom (ID as broom of air)</a></li><li><a href="http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/item.html?item=2792">Cyclops Toes</a></li><li><a href="http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/item.html?item=2894">Griffon Feather</a></li><li><a href="http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/item.html?item=3142">Star Ruby</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=2><b>Additional Zones:</b></span><li><a href=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/zones/Antonica/Najena.htm>Najena</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=2><b>Related Creatures:</b></span><li><a href=http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?id=2577>A Cyclops</a></li><li><a href=http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?id=331>A Griffin</a></li><li><a href=http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?id=2128>A Magician</a></li></ul></td></tr></td></tr></table>This item will increase size and power of a summoned Air Elemental (above level 34).  You need A Star Ruby, A Feather from a Griffon, A Broom (from a Magician in Najena or alligator in Cazic) and the toes of a Cyclops. </td></tr>
	 <tr><td id=rt valign=top>Reward(s):</td></tr>
